name: 60X80 Placeable Machine Shed
description: 3D tin, Occluders to make machinery disappear to improve performance when the building is all shut up with equipment inside, animated bi-fold electric winch door, animated lights, snow mesh on the roof. This file is set up with 15 different color combinations in the store. Can't find the color combo you want? No problem, these are easy to edit in GE. Unzip the file, open a building of your choice in GE and change the color combinations up as this building is set up on UDIM color select. You can just save the file you opened or you can save as a new file name, copy and rename an existing xml, and add the xml name to the mod desc and you have another option!
